section.jumbotron.jumbotron-primary
    .container.text-center
        h3 A Javascript library to power cart management for Shopify themes.
        p.lead
            a.btn.btn-lg.btn-outline-inverse(href="{{ 'cartjs.zip' | asset_url }}") Download Cart.js

section.jumbotron
    .container
        .row
            .col-md-6
                h3 What is Cart.js?
                != partial('../guide/sections/introduction/what')
            .col-md-6
                h3 Why should I use it?
                != partial('../guide/sections/introduction/why')

section.jumbotron
    .container
        .row
            .col-md-6
                h3 Okay, show me what it can do!

                p Sure! This site is actually hosted on Shopify, so we can see Cart.js in action right here.
                p Why not start by clicking one of the buttons below to add a product to your cart?

                .row.form-group
                    !="{% for product in collections.frontpage.products %}"
                    .col-xs-6
                        button.btn.btn-block.btn-default(data-cart-add="{{ product.variants.first.id }}") Add a {{ product.title | escape }}
                    !="{% endfor %}"
            .col-md-6
                != partial('sections/okay-show-me-table')

        .row
            .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
